window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Bureau of Preternatural Investigations returns in <i>Switchback</i>, the sequel to Melissa F. Olson's <i>Nightshades</i>.</b> </p> <p>Three weeks after the events of <i>Nightshades</i>, things are finally beginning to settle for the Chicago branch of the BPI, but the brief respite from the horror of the previous few weeks was never destined to last. </p> <p>The team gets a call from Switch Creek, WI, where a young man has been arrested on suspicion of being a shade. </p> <p>The suspect is held overnight, pending DNA testing, but seemingly escapes in a terrifying and bloody massacre. But is there more to the jailbreak than a simple quest for freedom? </p>"; 
